
    USE AT YOUR OWN RISK !
    
    This is experimental driver.. who knows what it'll do ;)
    
hints:

    * edit Makefile 
    * compile
    * become root and issue "make test"
    * start X
    * start xawtv
    * get xv_stream, compile it
    * run xv_stream --device=/dev/video0 
      (preferably over network from a different computer with Xv capable
      video card)
    * enjoy
    * tweak
    
